Caliburs ignores Tremor, instead transforming into his machine gun mode,
and landing on the tank, clamping himself down. He lets loose a barrage
of bullets towards the Dinobot who is killing his comerade. 

Grimlock first laughs at the machine gun bullets that almost meerly
bounce off his armor, but then a tank shell hits him dead centre, and he
is knocked back. He looks up, and smiles at the thought of the rampaging
Decepticon. "Good. Me not expect him to return."

Apeface looks around, wondering if he should risk Havotron's wrath by
leaving to help. "Do you need backup?" he asks, but knowing the awnser.
